🔹 Conditional Statements
Basic if statement
if [ condition ]then  commandsfi

Example
num=10if [ $num -gt 5 ]then  echo "Number is greater than 5"fi

if-else
num=3if [ $num -gt 5 ]then  echo "Greater"else  echo "Smaller"fi

if-elif-else
num=10if [ $num -lt 5 ]then  echo "Less than 5"elif [ $num -eq 10 ]then  echo "Equal to 10"else  echo "Greater than 5"fi

🔹 Hands-on Scripts
Check if service is running
