🔹 Functions
Syntax
Method 1
function myfunc {  echo "Hello from function"}
Method 2
myfunc() {  echo "Hello from function"}
Call Function
myfunc

Function Example
#!/bin/bashgreet() {  echo "Hello from function"}greet

Function with Arguments
#!/bin/bashgreet() {  echo "Hello $1"}greet Jatin

Multiple Arguments
